CASE
  WHEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0)) LIKE '%IPHONE%'
  THEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0))
  WHEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0)) LIKE '%ANDROID%'
  THEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0))
  WHEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0)) LIKE '%IPAD%'
  THEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0))
  WHEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0)) LIKE '%NEWS%'
  THEN 'DESKTOP'
  WHEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0)) LIKE '%WEB%'
  THEN 'DESKTOP'
  ELSE 'UNKNOWN'
END

CASE
  WHEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0)) LIKE '%NEWS%'
  THEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0))
  WHEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0)) LIKE '%WEB%'
  THEN UPPER(SPLIT_PART(TRIM("VIDEOTITLE"), '|', 0))
  ELSE 'UNKNOWN'
END
